fields.bio: With 4+ years of experience as a backend software engineer, I specialize in Python and SQL, focusing on API development, system architecture, and scalable solutions. fields.title: Gettik Asia - Transportation Platform

fields.title: Orienbank - Oriyonbusiness

fields.title: eDonish - School Digitalization Platform
